    "courseType": "major_elective",
    "prerequisites": "COMP3278",
    "exclusions": "None",
    "description": "The course will study some advanced topics and techniques in database systems, with a focus on the system and algorithmic aspects. It will also survey the recent development and progress in selected areas. Topics include: query optimization, spatial-spatiotemporal data management, multimedia and time-series data management, information retrieval and XML, data mining.",
    "sourceUrl": "https://www.cs.hku.hk/index.php/programmes/course-offered?infile=2025/comp3323.html",
