    "description": "Basics of character animation, keyframe animation, motion capture, inverse kinematics, physically based character animation, Basics of physically-based animation, rigid body dynamics, point-based dynamics, hair animation, cloth simulation, facial animation, crowd simulation, mesh-shape editing, performance capture, skinning, data-driven character control, data-driven cloth animation, data-driven facial animation, data-driven skinning.",
    "sourceUrl": "https://www.cs.hku.hk/index.php/programmes/course-offered?infile=2025/comp3360.html",
